dataList.content: <... Huh, yeah. How come there's a Lobotomy Corp. logo inside La Manchaland?>
Mm, now may not be the appropriate time, for too much is still veiled in mysteries to utter with certitude.
I tried to urge Yi Sang, who trailed off mid-explanation, to speak, but...
<... Okay. Let me know when you're more certain.>
... I'm sure he has a good reason for not sharing his suspicions at the moment. I nodded.
<Okay, then... let's get back on track and keep following Sancho.>
Abnormality or not, we still have a job to do.
